-1 'NEWBIE INFO'~
Be welcome oh adventurer.  Since you are new to the game, your best course
of action is to traverse the mud school before journeying on to other realms.
It's designed to help you learn the basics of the game.  Make sure you read
all the signs in the area, as they will add helpful hints on how things work.
Just north of you, you will find rooms to the east and west. Make sure you
visit them and follow the helps. To see a list of the Equipment you are
wearing, type: equipment. To see if you have spells to cast type: spells.
To see a list of your skills type: skills. For a list of available commands
type: commands.  To see basic information about yourself type: score.

* For new players:
     Don't try to kill the blob in mudschool.

To see a lot more useful information, type: help beginners
~

1 IGNORE~
Syntax: ignore
        ignore <character name>
        ignore nobody

Typing ignore by itself will show you a list of the people that you are ignoring.
Putting someone on your ignore list will prevent them from telling to you.  Typing
ignore nobody will clear your ignore list.

