8)  Try not to overrule each other.

9)  Trusted mortals:  Do not use your god powers to help your mortal
    character.  If you do, your trust will be taken away.

10) If your mortal character has a disagreement with a player, do not use
    your immortal to get even, in any way shape or form.  Keep your mortals
    and your immortal disassociated from one another.

