-1 LYCANTHROPY~
Lycanthropy is a magical disease out of legend, with the main affect on
the afflicted being that on the Full Moon, the diseased person turns into
a Were-Creature. The most commonly known form is the Were-Wolf. The
disease is transmitted by being bitten by a being that is already
afflicted with Lycanthropy. The first Were-Creature was probably created
by some kind of Curse long ago, and has mutated into it's current form.
Were-Creatures typically carry 1-4 items, depending on there size, and
have no worries about death. There is currently know known cure for this
disease.
